public class Solution {
  public ListNode removeElements(ListNode head, int target) {
    if(head == null) {
      return head;
    }
    ListNode dummy = new ListNode(0);
    dummy.next = head;
    ListNode prev = dummy;
    ListNode cur = head;
    while(cur != null) {
      if (cur.value != target) {
        cur = cur.next;
        prev = prev.next;
      } else {
        ListNode next = cur.next;
        prev.next = next;
        cur = next;
      }
    }
    return dummy.next;
  }
}


这道题虽然是easy但也有很多需要注意的地方，
1.  if(head == null) {
      return head;
    }
    判断语句不能加 head.next == null否则会rule out只有一个variable的情况
    
2. 加一个dummy就会轻松很多
